## Splunk Detection Dashboards Built During Investigation

### Dashboard 1: BEC Hunting Panel (SPL)

```spl
| multisearch
  [search index=o365_audit Operation="New-InboxRule" | eval type="Inbox Rule Created"]
  [search index=o365_audit Operation="MailItemsAccessed"
    | stats count by user | where count > 200 | eval type="Bulk Mail Access"]
  [search index=azure_ad ResultStatus="Success"
    | iplocation IPAddress | where Country!="India" | eval type="Foreign Login"]
| table _time, user, type, IPAddress, Country
| sort -_time
```

### Dashboard 2: Active Session Anomaly

```spl
index=azure_ad sourcetype=azure:aad:signin ResultStatus="Success"
| iplocation IPAddress
| eval risk_score=case(
    Country!="India", 50,
    ClientAppUsed="Browser" AND UserAgent LIKE "%HeadlessChrome%", 80,
    isnotnull(DeviceDetail.isCompliant) AND DeviceDetail.isCompliant="false", 40,
    true(), 0)
| where risk_score > 40
| table _time, user, IPAddress, Country, ClientAppUsed, risk_score
| sort -risk_score
```

