## Containment Actions

1. Revoked all active O365 sessions for `rmehra` via Azure AD
2. Blocked `185.220.101.12` and `company-invoiceportal.com` at proxy and email gateway
3. Deleted malicious inbox rule `AutoArchive_FIN`
4. Contacted bank — wire transfer frozen 40 minutes before execution
5. Notified CERT-In (mandatory reporting — financial sector)
6. Enforced FIDO2 hardware key MFA for all Finance and Executive accounts

