## Recommendations

| Finding | Recommendation |
|---------|---------------|
| AiTM bypassed SMS MFA | Enforce FIDO2/hardware token MFA for privileged and finance users |
| Inbox rule not alerted | Build Splunk alert: inbox rules created from foreign IPs |
| 11-day invoice window exploited | Implement dual-approval for all wire transfers above €10,000 |
| No mail flow anomaly detection | Deploy Microsoft Defender for Office 365 — BEC detection policy |
| Phishing domain not blocked | Subscribe to threat intel feed; auto-block newly registered lookalike domains |
